    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "If you make a call with a deadline and the hostname fails to resolve before the call's deadline, the call should fail with a deadline expired status.\n\nThere is also a way to wait for the client to connect successfully with a deadline before making any calls, but the interface for that depends on what language you are using.\n"
